---
const lang = Astro.url.searchParams.get('lang') || 'ja';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang={lang}>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>安藤千英 | &LAB TOKYO — 発酵×ローフード 東京・渋谷</title>
  <meta name="description" content="ELLE gourmet認定料理家・安藤千英。東京・渋谷の発酵×ローフード ライフスタイルラボ。少人数制・初心者歓迎・¥8,000〜・入会費なし。体験レッスン受付中。" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    /* ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
       カラートークン（指示書準拠）
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ */
    :root {
      --bg0:  #1A1715;
      --bg1:  #1E1B19;
      --bg2:  #24211E;
      --bg3:  #2A2622;

      --txt:  #F3EEE5;
      --txth: #FAF5EC;
      --txts: #C0B6A8;
      --txtn: #D6CFC4;
      --div:  rgba(243,238,229,.12);

      --cta:  #C47A3A;
      --ctah: #D68B4A;
      --ctat: #12100F;

      --leaf: #4E8A18;

      --f-h: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Noto Sans JP', serif;
      --f-b: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--f-b);
      font-weight: 400;
      background: var(--bg0);
      color: var(--txt);
      line-height: 1.8;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ━━ ナビ ━━ */
    nav {
      position: fixed; inset: 0 0 auto 0; z-index: 500;
      height: 66px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 2.5rem;
      background: rgba(26,23,21,.93);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--div);
    }
    .nav-logo img { height: 42px; width: auto; }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.8rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--txtn);
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--cta); }
    .nav-cta {
      display: inline-block; margin-left: 1.5rem;
      padding: .5rem 1.4rem;
      background: var(--cta); color: var(--ctat);
      font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background .2s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--ctah); }
    .lang {
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      margin-left: 1.2rem;
      border-left: 1px solid var(--div);
      padding-left: 1rem;
    }
    .lang a {
      font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--txts);
      padding: 4px 8px;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .lang a.on { color: var(--cta); font-weight: 700; }
    .lang a:hover { color: var(--txtn); }

    /* ━━ Hero ━━
       portrait主役 — きれいすぎる左右分割にしない
    ━━ */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding-top: 66px;
    }
    .hero-photo {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .hero-photo img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover; object-position: 70% top;
      display: block;
    }
    .hero-photo::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(to right,  rgba(26,23,21,.88) 0%, rgba(26,23,21,.55) 50%, rgba(26,23,21,.1) 100%),
        linear-gradient(to top,    rgba(26,23,21,.6)  0%, transparent 40%);
    }
    .hero-body {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      max-width: 560px;
      padding: 0 5vw 7vh;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 3.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cta); margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-name {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--txts);
      margin-bottom: .3rem;
    }
    .hero-role {
      font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--txts); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--f-b);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.8rem);
      line-height: 1.4; color: var(--txth);
      margin-bottom: .8rem;
    }
    .hero h1 span {
      color: var(--leaf);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--txts); margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-desc {
      font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--txt); line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 2.8rem;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 1rem 2.8rem;
      background: var(--cta); color: var(--ctat);
      font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background .25s, transform .2s;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: var(--ctah); transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* ━━ 体験レッスン概要ストリップ ━━ */
    .trial-strip {
      background: var(--bg1);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--div);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--div);
      padding: 1.4rem 5vw;
    }
    .trial-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .trial-label {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: .7rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cta); white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .trial-items {
      display: flex; gap: 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
      list-style: none; flex: 1;
    }
    .trial-items li {
      font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--txtn);
      padding: .2rem 1.2rem;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--div);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .trial-items li:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
    .trial-items li:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .trial-link {
      font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--cta); text-decoration: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition: opacity .2s;
    }
    .trial-link:hover { opacity: .75; }

    /* ━━ セクション共通 ━━ */
    .sec { padding: 7rem 5vw; }
    .sec-eye {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cta); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: block;
    }
    .sec-h2 {
      font-family: var(--f-b);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.45; color: var(--txth);
    }
    .rule { width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--cta); margin: 1.8rem 0 2.5rem; }
    .inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .body-text {
      font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--txt); line-height: 2.1;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }
    .body-text strong { color: var(--txth); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ━━ Story ━━ */
    .story { background: var(--bg1); }
    .story-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 48% 1fr;
      gap: 5rem; align-items: start;
    }
    .story-img { overflow: hidden; }
    .story-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 480px;
      object-fit: cover; display: block;
    }
    .story-body { padding-top: .5rem; }
    .story-link {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--txts); text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(192,182,168,.3);
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: color .2s, border-color .2s;
    }
    .story-link:hover { color: var(--cta); border-color: var(--cta); }

    /* ━━ Programs（非均等） ━━ */
    .programs { background: var(--bg0); }
    .programs-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .prog-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto;
      gap: 3px; margin-top: 3.5rem;
    }
    .prog {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      text-decoration: none; display: block;
    }
    .prog:first-child { height: 520px; }
    .prog:not(:first-child) { height: 360px; }
    .prog img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform .8s ease; display: block; }
    .prog:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .prog-ov {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26,23,21,.9) 0%, rgba(26,23,21,.1) 60%);
      transition: background .3s;
    }
    .prog:hover .prog-ov { background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26,23,21,.95) 0%, rgba(26,23,21,.2) 60%); }
    .prog-body { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; padding: 2rem 2rem 2.2rem; }
    .prog-eye {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cta); margin-bottom: .6rem; display: block;
    }
    .prog h3 {
      font-family: var(--f-b);
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--txth); margin-bottom: .6rem;
    }
    .prog-detail { font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txt); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .prog-meta { font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--cta); }

    /* ━━ ブランド大型ビジュアル（h5） ━━ */
    .brand-visual {
      position: relative; height: 560px; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .brand-visual img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover; object-position: center 40%;
      display: block;
    }
    .brand-visual-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(26,23,21,.35);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .brand-visual-text {
      text-align: center; color: var(--txth);
    }
    .brand-visual-text p {
      font-family: var(--f-h);
      font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(243,238,229,.7); margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .brand-visual-text h2 {
      font-family: var(--f-b);
      font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.5; color: var(--txth);
    }

    /* ━━ Credentials ━━ */
    .credentials { background: var(--bg2); }
    .cred-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
      gap: 5rem; align-items: start;
    }
    .book-img img {
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .cred-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.8rem; }
    .cred-item {
      display: flex; gap: 1.4rem; align-items: flex-start;
      padding-bottom: 1.8rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--div);
    }
    .cred-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .cred-num {
      font-family: var(--f-h); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: italic;
      color: rgba(196,122,58,.3); flex-shrink: 0; width: 1.8rem; line-height: 1;
    }
    .cred-item h4 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--txth); margin-bottom: .35rem; }
    .cred-item p { font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txts); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* ━━ Testimonials（Custifyスタイル） ━━ */
    .testimonials { background: var(--bg1); }
    .testi-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.2rem; margin-top: 3.5rem;
    }
    .testi {
      background: var(--bg2);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      border-top: 2px solid rgba(196,122,58,.35);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center;
    }
    .testi-photo {
      width: 88px; height: 88px; border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover; object-position: top;
      margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
      border: 2px solid rgba(196,122,58,.25);
    }
    .testi-mark {
      font-family: var(--f-h); font-size: 2.8rem; line-height: .5;
      color: rgba(196,122,58,.3); margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block;
    }
    .testi-quote {
      font-size: .92rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--txt); line-height: 1.95;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem; flex-grow: 1;
    }
    .testi-sep { width: 28px; height: 1px; background: rgba(196,122,58,.3); margin: 0 auto 1.2rem; }
    .testi-name { font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--txth); }
    .testi-role { font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txts); margin-top: .3rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ━━ Journal ━━ */
    .journal { background: var(--bg0); }
    .journal-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .journal-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .journal-all {
      font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--txts); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .journal-all:hover { color: var(--cta); }
    .post-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .post {
      background: var(--bg1); padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color .3s, background .3s;
    }
    .post:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--cta); background: var(--bg2); }
    .post-cat {
      font-family: var(--f-h); font-size: .68rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cta); margin-bottom: .9rem; display: block;
    }
    .post h4 {
      font-size: .98rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--txth); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .post-date { font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txts); }

    /* ━━ CTA ━━ */
    .cta-sec {
      background: var(--bg2); text-align: center;
      padding: 8rem 5vw; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-sec::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(196,122,58,.05) 0%, transparent 65%);
    }
    .cta-inner { position: relative; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .cta-body {
      font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--txt); line-height: 2.1; margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem;
      background: var(--cta); color: var(--ctat);
      font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background .25s, transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--ctah); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(196,122,58,.25); }
    .cta-sub {
      display: block; margin-top: 1.4rem;
      font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txts);
      text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s;
    }
    .cta-sub:hover { color: var(--cta); }
    .cta-note { margin-top: 1.2rem; font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txts); }

    /* ━━ Footer ━━ */
    footer {
      background: #110E0B; padding: 5rem 5vw 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--div);
    }
    .footer-grid {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--div);
    }
    .footer-logo img { height: 38px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; }
    .footer-tag { font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txts); line-height: 1.9; }
    .footer-col h5 {
      font-family: var(--f-h); font-size: .68rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cta); margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem; }
    .footer-col a {
      font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 400;
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--txts); transition: color .2s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--ctah); }
    .footer-copy {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
      text-align: center; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(243,238,229,.2);
    }

    /* ━━ レスポンシブ ━━ */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      nav { padding: 0 1.2rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .nav-cta { margin-left: .8rem; }
      .lang { padding-left: .8rem; margin-left: .8rem; }
      .hero-body { padding: 0 1.5rem 6vh; max-width: 100%; }
      .trial-inner { gap: 1rem; }
      .trial-items li { padding: .2rem .8rem; }
      .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .story-img img { height: 300px; }
      .prog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .prog:first-child { height: 340px; }
      .prog:not(:first-child) { height: 280px; }
      .brand-visual { height: 380px; }
      .cred-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
      .testi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .post-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .sec { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
      .journal-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ナビ -->
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><img src="/logo-wide.png" alt="&LAB TOKYO" /></a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/lessons">レッスン</a></li>
        <li><a href="/hacco">Hacco LAB</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">安藤千英</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog">ブログ</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:info@andlabtokyo.com" class="nav-cta">体験レッスン</a>
      <div class="lang">
        <a href="?lang=ja" class={lang==='ja'?'on':''}>JP</a>
        <a href="?lang=en" class={lang==='en'?'on':''}>EN</a>
        <a href="?lang=zh" class={lang==='zh'?'on':''}>中</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ① Hero — portrait主役 -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-photo">
      <img src="/hero-portrait.jpg" alt="発酵創家 安藤千英" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-body">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Fermentation Creator · Tokyo Shibuya</p>
      <p class="hero-name">安藤 千英　Chie Ando</p>
      <p class="hero-role">ELLE gourmet認定料理家 ／ 発酵×ローフード研究家</p>
      <h1>
        これからの私を、<br />
        <span>美しく「醸す」。</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">— 細胞からデザインする、一生モノの心と体 —</p>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        忙しい毎日の中で、自分の体を後回しにしていませんか。<br />
        発酵×ローフードのクロス理論で、あなたの本来の輝きを取り戻す。
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:info@andlabtokyo.com" class="hero-cta">体験レッスンを予約する</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ② 体験レッスン概要ストリップ -->
  <div class="trial-strip">
    <div class="trial-inner">
      <span class="trial-label">Trial Lesson</span>
      <ul class="trial-items">
        <li>東京・渋谷</li>
        <li>オンライン対応</li>
        <li>少人数制（1〜4名）</li>
        <li>初心者歓迎</li>
        <li>¥8,000〜</li>
        <li>入会費なし</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:info@andlabtokyo.com" class="trial-link">詳しく見る →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ③ My Story -->
  <section class="sec story">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-img">
          <img src="/story-lesson.jpg" alt="&LAB TOKYO レッスン風景" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <span class="sec-eye">My Story</span>
          <h2 class="sec-h2">なぜ、私は食を伝えるのか。</h2>
          <div class="rule"></div>
          <p class="body-text">
            10年前の4月。娘が台所の熱湯を頭からかぶる大火傷を負いました。
            長期入院、複数回の手術。私は<strong>キッチンに立てなくなった。</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            そこから食を学び直しました。マクロビ、ローフード、発酵。
            食べることが娘を、そして私自身を、内側から再生させていった。
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            40代になったとき、更年期という新しい岐路に立ちました。
            そのとき改めて気づいたのです——<strong>「細胞から整える食」は、一生モノの武器だ</strong>、と。
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            忙しい女性が、食から自分を取り戻せる場所をつくりたい。
            それが&LAB TOKYOの原点です。
          </p>
          <a href="https://note.com/chieando/n/naa6e962de57b" target="_blank" class="story-link">
            全文をnoteで読む →
